data.Description: Ages 16+ Welcome With Valid ID DOORS: 7PM SHOW: 8PM Based on the latest local guidelines, attendees are no longer required to provide proof of negative COVID-19 test AND/OR vaccination for entry into this event. Be sure to check your venue website for the latest updates and guidelines as entry requirements are subject to change. You must be 16 years old or older with a valid ID to enter the Fillmore Auditorium. Valid ID must be government issued and contain your picture and birthdate. There is no entry for anyone under 16 years old!!
